description:
Building &amp; Managing Subscription Web Sites DVD by Bill Myers


[img]http://www.excite-marketing.com/dvdtoolbox/BMS-DVD.jpg[/img]


Building &amp; Managing Subscription Web Sites is one of a series of excellent DVDs from Bill Myers about inventing your own successful home-based business based on your own individual strengths. It covers topics related to growing your home-based business online using eBay. So you will be having fun whilst making great profit too.

&quot;One of the largest growing business areas today. You can have customers paying you monthly or yearly for services and products and generate regular turnover and profit easily. This DVD shows you how to do this.&quot;

Valuable Topics covered on this DVD include:

-Definition of Subscription Web Sites;
-Business model;
-Profit potential;
-Start up costs;
-Topic choices;
-Start up checklist;
-Pricing strategies;
-Design choices;
-Effective marketing;
-Automation tools;
-Success stories;
-Resources;
and much, much more.
